channel.title: Compiling error
channel.description:
Anytime I compile I get this error .\Java\Animable_Sub5.java:9: warning: Message is internal proprietary API and may be removed in a future release private final int anInt1606; note: .\Java\Class36.java uses unchecked or unsafe operations. Note: Recompile with -Xlint: unchecked for details. 1 warning Press any key to continue . . .
Does anyone know what I need to do to fix this?
